title: ignored_folders()
brief: Exclude Maildirs from maildir-mode.
seealso: global_mode
version: 0.13
----

<p>When in maildir-mode the screen consists of a list of Maildir folders.  These may be anavigated/explored.</p>
<p>Any folder matching an entry in <span class="tt">ignored_folders</span> will be excluded from the display, and will appear.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
ignored_folders = { "Archive.", "Backup." };
</pre>
<p>The default is to include all folders.</P>